snippet.title: Allen Pan - Sufficiently Advanced
snippet.description:
"Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic." -Arthur C. Clarke

My name's Allen, I try to make pretend things into real things. Also I failed at Mythbusters.

I get tons of emails, so I probably won't respond if you send one asking for build advice, sorry!

Culver City, CA, 90232
